<h2 class="bold font-l">A Communist Game of Telephone</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Everyone is so afraid to deliver bad news up the chain of command that a request for artillery support ends up completely lost. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GossipEvolution" class='trope-example-link'>Gossip Evolution</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
